snippet.title: Police: Amber Alert connected to fatal shooting of woman
snippet.description:
Milwaukee police have confirmed the disappearance of a 1-year-old boy, which sparked an Amber Alert early Monday morning, was connected to a fatal shooting at North 26th and Burleigh streets.
